column1: Does it have the ET Tube? What's the distance between the Carina and the ET Tube?
Is there nodules in this X-ray? Where is the nodule?
Is this X-ray contain any fractures?
What disease can you find in the left lung? Right lung?
Is the distance between the carina and the ET tube 5.6 mm?
Can you locate the Pleural effusion?
Is there pneumonia? Can you locate the Pneumonia?
